Finance Data EDA – Financial Behavior Analysis
Objective

This project performs exploratory data analysis (EDA) on financial behavior data to identify patterns in customer financial decisions, income levels, credit behavior, and investment preferences.

The goal is to uncover relationships between demographic variables and financial attributes to generate actionable business insights.

Dataset

Source: Kaggle – Finance Data Dataset
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/nitindatta/finance-data

The dataset contains demographic and financial attributes such as:

Age

Income

Credit behavior

Investment preferences

Financial product usage

Due to licensing restrictions, the dataset is not included in this repository.
Please download it directly from Kaggle using the link above.

